%% Skillsurge AI Platform - User Flow Diagrams

%% 1. Complete User Journey Flow
graph TD
    Start([Start]) --> Visit[Visit Platform]
    Visit --> Landing[Landing Page]
    Landing --> UserType{New/Returning?}
    
    %% New User Path
    UserType -->|New User| Register[Register Account]
    Register --> Assessment[Take Initial Assessment]
    Assessment --> Profile[Generate Learning Profile]
    Profile --> Recommendations[Course Recommendations]
    
    %% Returning User Path
    UserType -->|Returning User| Login[Login]
    Login --> Dashboard[Main Dashboard]
    
    %% Common Path
    Recommendations --> Dashboard
    Dashboard --> Activities{Choose Activity}
    
    %% Activity Paths
    Activities -->|Learn| Courses[Access Courses]
    Activities -->|Practice| Exercises[Do Exercises]
    Activities -->|Review| Flashcards[Use Flashcards]
    Activities -->|Test| Assessments[Take Assessments]
    
    %% Progress Tracking
    Courses --> Progress[Track Progress]
    Exercises --> Progress
    Flashcards --> Progress
    Assessments --> Progress
    
    Progress --> Goals{Goals Met?}
    Goals -->|Yes| Certificate[Earn Certificate]
    Goals -->|No| Dashboard

%% 2. Course Creation and Management Flow
graph LR
    Start([Start]) --> CreateCourse[Create Course]
    CreateCourse --> DefineGoals[Define Learning Goals]
    DefineGoals --> SelectTopic[Select Topic]
    SelectTopic --> SetParams[Set Parameters]
    SetParams --> Structure[Create Structure]
    Structure --> Review{Review}
    Review -->|Adjust| SetParams
    Review -->|Approve| Publish[Publish Course]
    Publish --> Monitor[Monitor Progress]
    Monitor --> Update{Update Needed?}
    Update -->|Yes| Revise[Revise Content]
    Update -->|No| Complete([Complete])
    Revise --> Review

%% 3. Learning Session Flow
graph TD
    Start([Start Session]) --> CheckDash[Check Dashboard]
    CheckDash --> Plan[Plan Session]
    Plan --> Choose{Choose Activity}
    
    Choose -->|Course| Course[Course Content]
    Choose -->|Practice| Practice[Practice Exercises]
    Choose -->|Review| Review[Flashcard Review]
    
    Course --> Complete[Complete Activity]
    Practice --> Complete
    Review --> Complete
    
    Complete --> Track[Track Progress]
    Track --> Achieve{Achievement?}
    Achieve -->|Yes| Badge[Earn Badge]
    Achieve -->|No| Next[Next Activity]
    Badge --> Next
    Next --> End([End Session])

%% 4. Assessment and Progress Flow
graph TD
    Start([Start Assessment]) --> Type{Assessment Type}
    
    Type -->|Knowledge Check| Quick[Quick Quiz]
    Type -->|Module Test| Module[Module Assessment]
    Type -->|Final| Final[Final Exam]
    
    Quick --> Score[Calculate Score]
    Module --> Score
    Final --> Score
    
    Score --> Analyze[Analyze Performance]
    Analyze --> Report[Generate Report]
    Report --> Recommend[Recommendations]
    
    Recommend --> Action{Next Action}
    Action -->|Review| Review[Review Material]
    Action -->|Advance| Next[Next Module]
    Action -->|Complete| Cert[Certificate]

%% 5. Support and Resource Access Flow
graph LR
    Start([Need Help]) --> Type{Help Type}
    
    Type -->|Quick Help| AI[AI Assistant]
    Type -->|Documentation| Docs[Help Docs]
    Type -->|Community| Forum[Community Forum]
    Type -->|Direct| Support[Support Team]
    
    AI --> Solution[Get Solution]
    Docs --> Solution
    Forum --> Solution
    Support --> Solution
    
    Solution --> Resolved{Resolved?}
    Resolved -->|Yes| Continue[Continue Learning]
    Resolved -->|No| Escalate[Escalate Issue]
    Escalate --> Support

%% 6. Interactive Learning Tools Flow
graph TD
    Start([Access Tools]) --> ToolType{Select Tool}
    
    ToolType -->|Flashcards| Cards[Flashcard System]
    ToolType -->|Practice| Exercise[Practice Engine]
    ToolType -->|Visual| Visual[Visual Tools]
    
    Cards --> Study[Study Session]
    Exercise --> Practice[Practice Session]
    Visual --> Learn[Learning Session]
    
    Study --> Track[Track Progress]
    Practice --> Track
    Learn --> Track
    
    Track --> Update[Update Profile]
    Update --> Suggest[Get Suggestions]
    Suggest --> Next[Next Session] 